# <CENTER> NODE JS
-  An Open source and cross platform js runtime environment
- Runs in single process without creating a new thread 
- Makes Js run on both client and server
- Fast Performance
- Lightweight

## Browsers VS Nodejs
- Browsers have access to DOM, Web API
- Nodejs has access to file system, OS


## Setup
    node -v to check version

npm also gets installed with nodejs to manage dependancies

    npm -v to check version